text: Anna Serme (born 15 May 1991 in Krnov), previously known as Anna Klimundová is a Czech professional squash player. As of February 2018, she was ranked number 82 in the world. She is married to French squash player Lucas Serme. ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Czech female squash players Category:People from Krnov Category:Competitors at the 2017 World Games
